{"word":"H3499 - יֶתֶר - yether - yeh'-ther - Abundant","slug":"H3499","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יֶתֶר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>yether"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yeh'-ther"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Abundant"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05EA;&#x05E8; - yether</b> - <i>yeh'-ther</i><p/>Properly an <i>overhanging</i>, that is, (by implication) an <i>excess</i>, <i>superiority</i>, <i>remainder</i>; also a small <i>rope</i> (as hanging free): -  + abundant, cord, exceeding, excellency (-ent), what they leave, that hath left, plentifully, remnant, residue, rest, string, with."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1956\">H1956</a>, <a href=\"#/H3148\">H3148</a>, <a href=\"#/H3492\">H3492</a>, <a href=\"#/H3498\">H3498</a>, <a href=\"#/H3500\">H3500</a>, <a href=\"#/H3501\">H3501</a>, <a href=\"#/H3502\">H3502</a>, <a href=\"#/H3503\">H3503</a>, <a href=\"#/H3504\">H3504</a>, <a href=\"#/H3505\">H3505</a>, <a href=\"#/H3506\">H3506</a>, <a href=\"#/H3507\">H3507</a>, <a href=\"#/H3508\">H3508</a>, <a href=\"#/H3509\">H3509</a>, <a href=\"#/H4195\">H4195</a>, <a href=\"#/H4340\">H4340</a>"}]}